Package: glockr
Title: Count Lines of Code Using 'scc'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "mjfrigaard@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R wrapper around the 'scc' (Succinct Code Counter)
    command-line utility <https://github.com/boyter/scc>. Counts lines of
    code, comments, and blank lines across many languages, with optional
    complexity metrics.  'scc' must be installed and available on the
    system PATH.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mjfrigaard/glockr,
    https://mjfrigaard.github.io/glockr/
BugReports: https://github.com/mjfrigaard/glockr/issues
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    processx,
    tibble
